<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Processes other than fire primarily disturb the stands. Disturbance typically initiates stands, including inundation followed by seasonal drying or by clearing of existing vegetation.</div>
